Meru Senator Mithika Linturi was arrested on Sunday for making remarks deemed as incitement. This is not the first time the senator is being arrested or involved in controversies. From his protracted divorce case to being charged with an attempted rape to his househelp dying mysteriously, Linturi's life has been a rollercoaster of sorts. From 2017 to the time he was being arrested over incitement allegations, Linturi has faced numerous court battles.